description: Lists the associations between a service network and a VPC endpoint.

parameters.name: serviceNetworkIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the service network associated with the VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Information about the association between the VPC endpoint and service network.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the association was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service network.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC endpoint associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointOwnerId
nested_items.description: The owner of the VPC endpoint associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: vpcId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC for the association.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, a pagination token for the next page of results.
